/* Table: "MD_Building" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "MD_Building"
(
"BuildingID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"BuildingCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"BuildingName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"BuildingArea" NUMBER(20, 4) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"MallID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
constraint PK_MD_BUILDING primary key ("BuildingID")
);

comment on column "MD_Building"."Enable" is
'1: 有效
0: 无效';

alter table "MD_Building"
add constraint FK_MD_BUILDING_2_MD_MALL_PK foreign key ("MallID")
references "MD_Mall" ("MallID");
